Subject: RE: Epstein investigation documents 
Hi =, 
and I are the AUSAs working with on the Epstein investigation, and we wanted to briefly be in 
touch because mentioned there's some concern about having our office manage documents with a vendor (for 
scanning, cataloguing, and indexing), and she said it would be helpful for us to provide some examples of cases where 
that has been done in the past. We have a number of examples, and we're hoping to quickly chat with you about the 
most productive way to get that info to you—is there a good time for us to give you a call sometime early next week? 
We're happy to work around your schedule, and we really appreciate the help. 
EFTA00009931

Thanks very much, and talk soon, 
Assistant U.S. Attorney 
Southern District of New York 
EFTA00009932
